snippet.title: Assault Spy - Announcement Trailer (Steam)
snippet.description:
Early Access starts May 2018 on Steam!
     
Check out the Steam page here @ http://store.steampowered.com/app/767930/Assault_Spy/
Learn more @ http://www.AssaultSpy.com

Uncover the dark secrets of the Negabot mega corporation as you save the company from a hostile takeover. Assault Spy is a stylish, fast paced, pure-action game with a dash of comedy.
